<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:tc="http://farelogix.com/flx/tc" xmlns:air="http://farelogix.com/flx/AirShoppingRQ">
  <soapenv:Header>
    <tc:TransactionControl>
      <tc>
        <app version="90" language="en-US">SOAPFLX</app>
        <iden u="Travelport1G" p="cX3v9PFojXSD23Vc" pseudocity="AHO8" agt="xmltvp001" agtpwd="4z333IQ6" agtrole="Ticketing Agent" agy="00567394"/>
        <agent user="xmltvp001"/>
        <trace>skwok-trace</trace>
        <script engine="FLXDM" name="travelport-qf-dispatch.flxdm"/>
      </tc>
    </tc:TransactionControl>
  </soapenv:Header>
  <soapenv:Body>
    <air:FlxTransaction>
      <!--send @Version="17.2" for IATA NDC v.17.2; generate random @TransactionIdentifier-->

        <PointOfSale>
          <Location>
            <CountryCode>{{gctry_cde}}</CountryCode>
            <CityCode>{{gcty_cde}}</CityCode>
          </Location>
        </PointOfSale>

        <Document id="document"/>

        <Party>
        <Sender>
                	<TravelAgencySender>
                    		<Name>TVP</Name>
                    		<Type>TravelAgency</Type>
                    		<PseudoCity>XD8</PseudoCity>
                    		<IATA_Number>99899992</IATA_Number>
                    		<AgencyID>99899992</AgencyID>
                    		<AgentUser>
                        		<AgentUserID>travelport</AgentUserID>
                    		</AgentUser>
                		</TravelAgencySender>
        		  </Sender>
        </Party>       

        <CoreQuery>
          <OriginDestinations>
            <!--list of OriginDestinations-->
            <OriginDestination OriginDestinationKey="OD1">
              <Departure>
                <AirportCode>{{gd_apcde_o}}</AirportCode>
                <Date>{{gd_date_o}}</Date>
              </Departure>
              <Arrival>
                <AirportCode>{{ga_apcde_o}}</AirportCode>
              </Arrival>
            </OriginDestination>                 

            <OriginDestination OriginDestinationKey="OD2">
              <Departure>
                <AirportCode>{{gd_apcde_i}}</AirportCode>
                <Date>{{gd_date_i}}</Date>
              </Departure>
              <Arrival>
                <AirportCode>{{ga_apcde_i}}</AirportCode>
              </Arrival>
            </OriginDestination>

          </OriginDestinations>
        </CoreQuery>
        <Preference>
          <AirlinePreferences>
            <Airline>
              <AirlineID>QF</AirlineID>
            </Airline>
          </AirlinePreferences>
          
          <FarePreferences>
            <Types>
              <Type>749</Type>
              <Type>70J</Type>
            </Types>
          </FarePreferences>
        </Preference>
      
        <DataLists>
          <PassengerList>
            <Passenger PassengerID="T1">
              <PTC>ADT</PTC>
            </Passenger>
          </PassengerList>
        </DataLists>
      </AirShoppingRQ>
    </air:FlxTransaction>
  </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

header.description: A HSTS Policy informing the HTTP client how long to cache the HTTPS only policy and whether this applies to subdomains.

header.name: X-Content-Type-Options
header.description: The only defined value, "nosniff", prevents Internet Explorer from MIME-sniffing a response away from the declared content-type

header.name: X-Frame-Options
header.description: Clickjacking protection: "deny" - no rendering within a frame, "sameorigin" - no rendering if origin mismatch

header.name: X-XSS-Protection
header.description: Cross-site scripting (XSS) filter

<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:tc="http://farelogix.com/flx/tc" xmlns:air="http://farelogix.com/flx/AirShoppingRQ">
   <soapenv:Header>
      <tc:TransactionControl>
         <!--credentials-->
         <tc>
            <app version="999" language="en-US">SOAPFLX</app>
            <iden u="Farelogix" p="TEMP02" pseudocity="AHD6" agt="Koushik" agtpwd="Navekove123" agtrole="Ticketing Agent" agy="00567420"/>
            <agent user="Koushik"/>
            <trace>kn-traceone</trace>
            <script engine="FLXDM" name="qf-dispatch.flxdm"/>
         </tc>
         <!--/credentials-->
      </tc:TransactionControl>
   </soapenv:Header>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <air:FlxTransaction>
         <!--send @Version="17.2" for IATA NDC v.17.2; generate random @TransactionIdentifier-->
         <AirShoppingRQ Version="17.2" TransactionIdentifier="c03ccc50-0597-40bd-a">
            <Document id="document"/>
            <Party>
               <Sender>
                  <TravelAgencySender>
                     <PseudoCity>AHD6</PseudoCity>
                     <AgencyID>00567420</AgencyID>
                  </TravelAgencySender>
               </Sender>
            </Party>
            <CoreQuery>
               <OriginDestinations>
                  <!--list of OriginDestinations-->
                  <OriginDestination OriginDestinationKey="OD1">
                     <Departure>
                        <AirportCode>AKL</AirportCode>
                        <Date>2018-11-01</Date>
                     </Departure>
                     <Arrival>
                        <AirportCode>SYD</AirportCode>
                     </Arrival>
                  </OriginDestination>
               </OriginDestinations>
            </CoreQuery>
            <Preference>
               <FarePreferences>
                  <Types>
                     <!--70J - Published Fares only; 749 - Negotiated Fares only; both 70J and 749 - Published and Negotiated Fares-->
                     <Type>749</Type>
                     <Type>70J</Type>
                  </Types>
               </FarePreferences>
               <FlightPreferences>
                  <Aircraft>
                     <Classes>
                        <Class>D</Class>
                     </Classes>
                  </Aircraft>
               </FlightPreferences>
            </Preference>
            <DataLists>
               <PassengerList>
                  <!--list of passengers-->
                  <Passenger PassengerID="T1">
                     <PTC>ADT</PTC>
                     <Individual>
                        <GivenName>ROBERT</GivenName>
                        <Surname>ABBEY</Surname>
                     </Individual>
                  </Passenger>
                  <Passenger PassengerID="T2">
                     <PTC>CHD</PTC>
                  </Passenger>
                  <Passenger PassengerID="T3">
                     <PTC>INF</PTC>
                  </Passenger>
               </PassengerList>
            </DataLists>
         </AirShoppingRQ>
      </air:FlxTransaction>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

header.name: X-Content-Type-Options
header.description: The only defined value, "nosniff", prevents Internet Explorer from MIME-sniffing a response away from the declared content-type

header.description: Clickjacking protection: "deny" - no rendering within a frame, "sameorigin" - no rendering if origin mismatch

header.description: Cross-site scripting (XSS) filter
